• @romakhannaofficial Golden Hour Glow for the Mehendi Bride ✨

For this mehendi glam, the focus was on radiant, skin-like base makeup — luminous highlights, soft contouring, and that ethereal bridal glow ✨. 

The eyes were softly smoked with a delicate wing, and we added a tinge of green on the lower lash line to tie in with the outfit — subtle, yet striking♥️

Defined brows and a juicy nude gloss brought the whole look together with elegance✨

This timeless glam complements the regal deep green lehenga from @labelnityabajaj with intricate detailing, and how stunning is this statement jewellery by @vaidaan.official Perfectly balancing tradition with trend♥️
